tle> Maxing perforate artery for infiltrator</span><hr size=1> So far, I got 705.<br><br>With bonuses I have 50 CS, 50 thrust<br>Using Shimmering arcanium guarded rapier:<br>16.4/3.5.  Effective dps: 15.8 I believe.<br><br>Even buffed, the 705 seems to be the limit.  I'm not talking the ( ) numbers, I'm talking the final damage output not in parenthesis.<br><br>I'm guessing try to get a higher quality rapier for a higher effective dps.<br><br>Was wondering if having 50+ thrust and 50+ CS helps push perfs higher.<br><br>With respec I plan to shave off unnecesary points from envenom (it can reach 54 now) and throw more into my raw thrust skill.   I love using lifebane, so I prolly won't push my thrust to a raw 50 for the uber stun, however.<br><br>Thanks, <p>Krelios<BR>Infiltrator<BR>Blackfist Clan<BR></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ukrelios.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Krelios</A> at: 5/15/02 12:32:04 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usaladgroovebust.showPublicProfile?language=EN>saladgroovebust</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/15/02 8:18:28 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm22.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=200.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Maxing perforate artery for infiltrator</span><hr size=1> If you stun (ie creeping death) does that mean if a DOT poison prots then it breaks the stun?<br>If so what poisons dont break the stun?<br><br>Oh and I was also wondering if having 50+ thrust and 50+ CS helps push perfs higher. <br><!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span cl